reviewText: Great price for 4 movies. Only interested in some of them, but the price is too good to pass up.
Becoming Jane was worth it, but the others were a bit of an old story. The other movies were filmed like back in the 80's so I wasn't too thrilled.
Liked the Jane Eyre movies, Basquiat was a little confusing, and St Ives is a light harded comical movie. This one is great for a raining day.
